    %h1 About Hunt Awesome
    %h3 Scavenger Hunt Your Way to Fun
    %p 
      Hunt Awesome is a FREE service created to provide our users with the most Awesome month of their lives. By completing a series of fun and exciting tasks in a scavneger hunt style manor, you will naturally begin do Awesome things, be more Awesome, and make other feel Awesome all at the same time. The beauty is that these small tasks are meant to be easy to integrate into your normal day and weeks. The challenges are a combination of tasks
      %i you know you should do but don't, simply forget to stop and appreciate, or tasks you never would have known you love in the first place.
      %b The end result of the process is a documented month where that you can remember as the Awesome-ess ever!
    %h3 The Team
    %p Our team originally got together to create www.getacluecrawls.com, a bar crawl scavenger hunt service, that takes bachelor(ette), birthday, and corporate parties on a fun evening of bar hopping and clue solving.
    %p 
      From this experience, we learned how enjoyable a 3-4 hour event can be for the participants. The happiness they exuded started from the moment they booked the service, through the event itself, all the way to months after as they reminisced on the fun they had. The notes we received from participants that had crawled up to year before was incredible. 
      %b It was in a single word - inspiring. 
      So we set out on mission to figure out a way to provide that same amazing feeling our bar crawl scavenger hunts gave to people but this time let them experience it over an even longer period of time. HuntAwesome is that child of that mission.
